      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2653 - Al-Hasan al-Sayqal asked Abu Abdullah (as) about a Muhrim whose tooth is causing him pain: \"Can he have it extracted?\"\nImam (as) said: \"Yes, there is no harm in it.\""
